12. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
14. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
15. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
16. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
